INSERT INTO `mac_vod` VALUES('19890','大汉天子2','','dahantianzi2','D','','http://puui.qpic.cn/vcover_vt_pic/0/wlmdneavviglkqnt1447554638.jpg/220','http://puui.qpic.cn/vcover_vt_pic/0/wlmdneavviglkqnt1447554638.jpg/220','','黄晓明 宁静 王刚 李立 董勇 刘晓虎 何佳怡 杜淳','董力','黄晓明,汉武帝,霍去病,东方朔,主父偃','','大陆','国语','0','12','',',1067,','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','434642','0','0','0','0','0','0','8.0','0','247','1481739574','1482086330','0','0','本剧集故事承接第一部剧情，讲述汉武帝刘彻（黄晓明饰）经过五年执政后进入他实施雄才大略阶段的故事。已坐稳皇帝宝座的刘彻，此时却触景生情，感慨当年亲如手足的兄弟们多已不在人世，唯一仍在人世的李勇（杜淳饰）却陷落匈奴手中，东方朔也一去不复返。\n历经千难万险寻找李勇下落的秋蝉（刘芸饰），终于在匈奴找到他时却发现他已与匈奴公主成婚。汉武帝微服出游，邂逅长相酷似已逝的陈阿娇的歌伎李娃（何佳怡饰），不禁怜爱有加。不久李娃入宫成为刘彻的新宠。然而已为皇后的卫子夫（宁静饰）却预见陈阿娇的前车之鉴又要重演。汉武帝派汲黯（杨洪武饰）去寻访东方朔，无意间遇见了怀才不遇的狂士主父偃（王刚饰），认为是奇才，遂力荐主父偃入宫辅佐汉武帝。汉武帝听信谗言，将卫青（董勇饰）的兵权交给霍去病（李立饰）。\n        ','qq','','','01$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/wlmdneavviglkqn/g0018fto9tq.html#02$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/wlmdneavviglkqn/z00126u0kxd.html#03$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/wlmdneavviglkqn/z0012m1n0mh.html#04$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/wlmdneavviglkqn/g0012syuh0d.html#05$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/wlmdneavviglkqn/r0012g3d0f4.html#06$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/wlmdneavviglkqn/m0012uej4br.html#07$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/wlmdneavviglkqn/j0012rti605.html#08$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/wlmdneavviglkqn/c0019p31i0s.html#09$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/wlmdneavviglkqn/n0012m6rp1k.html#10$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/wlmdneavviglkqn/m0012d2n38u.html#11$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/wlmdneavviglkqn/d00129yna5z.html#12$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/wlmdneavviglkqn/i0012h43t3r.html#13$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/wlmdneavviglkqn/q001200f23v.html#14$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/wlmdneavviglkqn/y0012un9zhg.html#15$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/wlmdneavviglkqn/h00122x3oc4.html#16$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/wlmdneavviglkqn/x0012n1y0kh.html#17$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/wlmdneavviglkqn/z0012ml61cz.html#18$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/wlmdneavviglkqn/v001204unug.html#19$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/wlmdneavviglkqn/o0012ifofjc.html#20$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/wlmdneavviglkqn/i0012j8ce72.html#21$http://v.q